{"tid":874114,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"數據顯示美國散戶愈跌愈溝。","createTime":"2018-10-24T02:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T02:54:52.000Z","uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0912f13f4becba94b13b22c596b9fa396208e322","tid":874114,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:54:52.000Z","msg":"美國股民撼大戶　嘉信策略師︰希望散戶懂得恐懼！<br />\n<br />\n美股周二(23日)大幅波動，道指一度挫逾500點，收市跌幅收窄至約百點。據美銀總計客戶資金流量數據顯示，散戶上周買進股票金額升至5月底以來最高水平，並為連續第3周買入；而機構和對沖基金則是賣出。 <br />\n<br />\n分析指，雖然這只反映了一家公司的客戶，但最近的拋售潮散戶又一次逢低買進，因為企業盈利增長20%，股票估值下降。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181024/mobile/bkn-20181024092734414-1024_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181024%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181024092734414-1024_00842_001.html&d=gdSRabkEe1ynn%2FDb2mZ3o%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0a5f3993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181024/mobile/bkn-20181024092734414-1024_00842_001.html</a>"}]}